{"tid":2227223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廣東海警再破粵港偷渡案拘12人　縝密偵查2個月後採取行動","createTime":"2020-10-02T15:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T16:13:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"33838965e28df15f216b84dd648afd27630fe012","tid":2227223,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201002/388817577775861760.jpeg/u1Q_hPndQMBwma_j7YZC8Rafyn07ZknCduT4M3bk-DM?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201002%2F388817577775861760.jpeg%2Fu1Q_hPndQMBwma_j7YZC8Rafyn07ZknCduT4M3bk-DM%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=a95f0676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/531144/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%B5%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%86%8D%E7%A0%B4%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E5%81%B7%E6%B8%A1%E6%A1%88%E6%8B%9812%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B8%9D%E5%AF%86%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A52%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%8C%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F531144%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%258B%259812%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%25B8%259D%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%259F%25A52%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%258E%25A1%25E5%258F%2596%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=73218be0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/531144/%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E6%B5%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%86%8D%E7%A0%B4%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E5%81%B7%E6%B8%A1%E6%A1%88%E6%8B%9812%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B8%9D%E5%AF%86%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A52%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%8C%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95</a><br />\n<br />\n中國海警今日（10月2日）發布消息稱，9月29日，廣東海警局聯合深圳等地公安機關，統籌指揮中山、惠州、汕尾等沿海市海警局，在三地開展集中收網行動，偵破一宗組織他人偷越國（邊）境案件。<br />\n截止目前，海警共拘捕12名涉案人員，其中涉嫌組織運送者5名、偷渡人員7名，查扣涉案車輛1台、涉案快艇2艘。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，上述組織他人偷渡的犯罪集團長期活躍於粵港等地，採取「螞蟻搬家」的方式，利用快艇在粵東沿海地區組織人員偷渡境外，組織嚴密、分工明確。根據掌握的線索，廣東海警局在7月下旬成立專案組深入偵查。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，經過2個月縝密偵查，廣東海警聯合公安部門偵破該案，搗破這個長期組織人員偷渡的犯罪集團，切斷了兩條海上運輸通道，持續保持粵港海域的安全穩定。目前案件仍在偵辦中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201002/388766153356480512.jpeg/OO9hueEmLNoBWVbMK8VlGHj4yxerIfQfdDqlHnQ6pR4?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201002%2F388766153356480512.jpeg%2FOO9hueEmLNoBWVbMK8VlGHj4yxerIfQfdDqlHnQ6pR4%3Fv%3Dw480&h=d5dc9acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據介紹，為嚴防新冠肺炎疫情從海上輸入，廣東海警局自8月起密切與香港警方開展警務合作，對粵港海域偷渡犯罪活動保持嚴打高壓態勢，曾先後於8月4日、8月8日偵破2宗粵港跨境偷渡案，拘捕35名涉案疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n其後，廣東海警又於8月23日在其管轄海域內查獲一艘涉嫌非法越境船隻，海警登船後發現12名港人，有關人士涉嫌干犯「偷越國（邊）境罪」被捕。經初步調查後，深圳鹽田公安局刑事拘留12人，以作深入調查。<br />\n<br />\n及至9月30日，深圳市鹽田區人民檢察院通報「12名港人偷渡案」，以涉嫌組織他人偷越邊境罪批准逮捕犯罪嫌疑人鄧某某、喬某某，以涉嫌偷越邊境罪批准逮捕犯罪嫌疑人李某某、黃某某等10人。該案仍在偵查中。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）"},{"pid":"182008e04d74686e077d12e127ea8c8f67e42ea0","tid":2227223,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"又拉多七個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057e691a82fadb5a8839baa3229a497db7eb1ed8","tid":2227223,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c73dcaf57abd41e0d4872c41677bdf6e5fddac8","tid":2227223,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，係咪黑警運人出海送中都未知"},{"pid":"e343225412f946a7c6669f6